"title": "8836: unbelief, as response to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8836: unbelief, as response to god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The stubborn and sinful refusal to accept God's word and his messengers. Since the coming of Jesus Christ it is frequently expressed in the rejection of his person and teaching.</p>\n<h2>Unbelief expressed towards God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:22\">PSA 78:22</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Rebellion against God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:14-2Kgs17:15\">2KI 17:14–17:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:16\">NEH 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:17-Ps78:19\">PSA 78:17–78:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:8-Ps95:11\">PSA 95:8–95:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:2\">ISA 65:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:26\">JER 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51\">ACT 7:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12-Heb3:19\">HEB 3:12–3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God's promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:24\">PSA 106:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:20\">ROM 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:16\">ROM 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:2\">HEB 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Unbelief expressed towards Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Rejection by those close to him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:11\">JHN 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54-Matt13:58\">MAT 13:54–13:58</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:1-Mark6:6\">MRK 6:1–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14-Luke4:30\">LUK 4:14–4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:5\">JHN 7:5</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of his miracles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22-Matt12:24\">MAT 12:22–12:24</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:22\">MRK 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:14-Luke11:16\">LUK 11:14–11:16</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of his claims</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:67\">LUK 22:67</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:37-John5:38\">JHN 5:37–5:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:36\">JHN 6:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:64\">JHN 6:64</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:24-John10:26\">JHN 10:24–10:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:7\">1PE 2:7</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of his words</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:11-John3:12\">JHN 3:11–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:46-John5:47\">JHN 5:46–5:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:45\">JHN 8:45</a></p>\n<h3>Demands for miraculous signs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:48\">JHN 4:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:38-Matt12:39\">MAT 12:38–12:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:29\">LUK 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:4\">MAT 16:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:12\">MRK 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:16\">LUK 11:16</a></p>\n<h2>Unbelief expressed towards God's messengers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:16\">GEN 19:16</a> <em>Lot</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:1\">EXO 4:1</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:2\">2KI 7:2</a> <em>Elisha</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:15\">2CH 32:15</a> <em>Sennacherib of Assyria urges the inhabitants of Jerusalem to disbelieve Hezekiah's words</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:1\">ISA 53:1</a> <em>Isaiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:32\">MAT 21:32</a> <em>John the Baptist</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:50\">ACT 13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:2\">ACT 14:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:13\">ACT 17:13</a> <em>Paul and Silas</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:9\">ACT 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:24\">ACT 28:24</a></p>\n<h2>Unbelief expressed in unrighteousness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:15\">TIT 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">ROM 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:12\">2TH 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:2\">2TH 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:13\">1TI 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>Unbelief despite miraculous signs</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:16-Neh9:17\">NEH 9:16–9:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:8-Exod4:9\">EXO 4:8–4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:32\">PSA 78:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:18\">JHN 9:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:31-John10:33\">JHN 10:31–10:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:37\">JHN 12:37</a></p>\n<h2>Means of overcoming unbelief</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:37-John10:38\">JHN 10:37–10:38</a> <em>the evidence of Jesus Christ's miracles</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:14–10:15</a> <em>preaching the gospel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:22-1Cor14:24\">1CO 14:22–14:24</a> <em>prophecy in worship</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1\">1PE 3:1</a> <em>the behaviour of a believing spouse</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:13\">1TI 1:13</a> <em>God's mercy</em></p>",
